[Change Player's Height]
author=bungholio
description=It only affects your appearance. It is kind of funny to mess with. If you keep subtracting you&#039;ll invert your character in a weird way. Inverting the height will cause him to look like a dog with it&#039;s butt in the air and face on the ground following a scent&#039;s trail.
