[Change your character to look more like a zombie at the end of the game]
author=bungholio
description=If x is b, c, d, e, or f, your character&#039;s hair will be black. But the game also froze everytime I tried to go into time trial mode, and I was lazy. I could have probably just tried it as an 8-bit code by changing the first digit to 0 instead of 2 because that could probably make it work perfectly, but I was lazy.

I didn&#039;t try, but I bet this would work if the code was 012D9BC0 0000000X instead.
patch=1,EE,212D9BC0,extended,00000008

