[Player Damage Modifier (or it's a damage multiplier?)]
author=bungholio
description=First thing to always do, never forget to put this line as the first line of the code. That&#039;s not my code, I got that from www.cmgsccc.com (CMX hacked it).
E00xE264 01358290

Make sure for x you put how many lines of code are after it.
For example, to modify your damage to 50 you would have this:
E001E264 01358290
212d9824 42480000

Have all Items equipped would be this:
E002E264 01358290
212DA3E0 FFFFFFFF
212DA3E4 FFFFFFFF

These all are, but I&#039;m very sure they are all in 32-bit floating point decimal, so I&#039;ll post some of those values afterwards because people have told me they had problems with this code, and I&#039;m assuming that&#039;s because I had it set to 1000. Just pick any 1 of these and put in the value.

And these are values

447A0000 = 1000
43FA0000 = 500
42C80000 = 100
42480000 = 50
41a00000 = 20
41200000 = 10
40A00000 = 5
40000000 = 2
patch=1,EE,212D9824,extended,212D982C
patch=1,EE,212D9834,extended,212D983C
patch=1,EE,212D9844,extended,212D984C
patch=1,EE,212D9854,extended,212D985C
patch=1,EE,212D9864,extended,212D986C
patch=1,EE,212D9874,extended,212D987C
patch=1,EE,212D9884,extended,212D988C
patch=1,EE,212D9894,extended,212D989C
patch=1,EE,212D98A4,extended,212D98AC
patch=1,EE,212D98B4,extended,00000000

