[Re-enable Debug Menus [View Note]]
author=punk7890
description=With the code on, while in game, press the following on controller #1 to enable debug menus:

*Select for ADPCM Test.
*L3 for gazeparamediter
*R3 for Light Editor.

On controller #2, you can also press R2 + X to spawn Agro anywhere. Agro will then drop down from the sky at your position.
