[Start game Standing]
author=bungholio
description=It&#039;s for you if you hate waiting 5 seconds for the guy to get up after you load a game you saved somewhere.
It might specifically be 012D9B53 00000000, because 212D9B50 4000000 made you start the game in the sitting position no matter what.
patch=1,EE,212D9B50,extended,00000000

[Player Codes\Super Jump [Hold triangle]]
author=
description=*Change the jump rate line to the following if you want:
200B1110 3C29xxxx
3c23 = super jump
3dcc = extreme jump
3f80 = you're going to fall for a while
