[Unlock Time Trial Mode]
author=bungholio
description=With this, the time trial mode is always opened, and the game never acts like it&#039;s the first time where the spirits tell you what all the buttons do.
Set it to 0 to not have access to time trial mode, not that you&#039;d want to.
patch=1,EE,D1BD9D3B,extended,E4F06C75
patch=1,EE,01EAD73C,extended,0000000E
patch=1,EE,11E024FA,extended,0000E87E
patch=1,EE,3020178C,extended,01467C42

